  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening the agri-base of the SACCO</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;Background proposed actions and choices made: CPF INEZA (Cooperative of Progress and Financing) is a SACCO with members classified as follows: 2761 females  4078 males and 711. It is based in the Southern Province  Muhanga and Kamonyi Districts. it&#x2019;s a growing SACCO. Agriterra has decided to partner with SACCOs in rural areas to resolve the issue of lack of finance for farmers. It is in this regard that  in November 2019  the team from Agriterra assessed CPF INEZA. Impamba is a successful SACCO which has entered the growth stage of its development trajectory  but this growth could be accelerated if the SACCO could strengthen its internal capital position  its savings  its credit product portfolio and its internal procedures. By supporting Impamba in this trajectory  external financing will be easier accessible for the SACCO. &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;The goal is to support the COOPEC to strengthen its agri-base.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-f-id=&quot;pbf&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Powered by &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1&quot; title=&quot;Froala Editor&quot;&gt;Froala Editor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
